      "description": "About Amelia Aesthetics introduces a patient-centered plastic surgery, medspa, and wellness practice dedicated to providing compassionate, personalized care through every stage of the patient journey. Founded on the belief that exceptional results begin with listening, Amelia combines advanced surgical expertise, evidence-based treatments, transparent education, and a supportive care experience designed to help patients make confident, informed decisions. With locations across the United States, Amelia brings together experienced surgeons, wellness providers, and care teams who share a commitment to empathy, safety, collaboration, and long-term results. From consultation through recovery, Amelia focuses on creating an individualized experience that helps patients achieve their goals while feeling heard, supported, and empowered.",
